  "description": "Tide in auto-filter mode (mode 2) at 0.18 Hz is the rhythmic engine of this patch — granular sustain tones breathe with a slow filter sweep that no LFO inside OPAL can replicate. The Tide stereo phase offset at 90 degrees creates a rotating, ocean-depth oscillation.",
